p.d: With: Brahim Asloum, boxer and actor; Olivier Delacroix, presenter; Samuel Étienne, presenter and journalist; Jérémy Ferrari, comedian; Virginie Hocq, comedian; Marine Lorphelin, Miss France 2013. The "Stars de Champagne" charity, formed by top athletes, organises gala matches in aid of children in hospital. Presented by: Olivier Minne (season 29, France, 2018)
